{"tid":252888,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(睡眠問題)救命 再係咁就顛","createTime":"2017-05-22T02:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T14:04:20.000Z","uid":88147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d731a5d2ff8e5bada6ab5b05a4bdf684c8851ef8","tid":252888,"uid":88147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"背景 21歲仔 做緊廢青 <br />\n發覺呢幾年成日都咁夜訓 搞到自己精神無咁好<br />\n同埋想變健康啲 所以最近三日都11點落床 目標730-800起身(訓8.5鐘左右)<br />\n但問題黎啦<br />\n平時極少發夢既我 呢三日都有發夢 <br />\n搞到好似無乜點精神到咁<br />\nAlarm響果陣 都係好唔想起身(未訓夠咁)<br />\n今日仲離譜 訓到岩岩945先起身 (訓左差唔多成11個鐘)<br />\n點解會咁早訓都訓到咁耐 <br />\n唉 我而家好嬲自己 覺得好浪費時間"},{"pid":"cae45c79412a5589649fcb7baaf48883812e3f7c","tid":252888,"uid":28369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"你都話你做緊廢青<br />\n<br />\n廢青咁早起身托？"},{"pid":"461dbbeba5f5870a95114c534024c22242d86ee6","tid":252888,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"強迫症.."},{"pid":"c623fa2a9f3d288efdb6c99687beec874b583694","tid":252888,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3359376d2ad035ebb5cd5ee992c3ec1e4e771af","tid":252888,"uid":88147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"廢青又唔係夜青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5187fdee302230c70738d1264d99163fe850ac99","tid":252888,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"雙失?"},{"pid":"5473155c9c12396f8c048b508002d6ccf479cbdd","tid":252888,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"橫掂做緊廢青, 有冇試過瞓到自然醒(唔理爬唔爬到起身, 淨計擘開眼)?<br />\n計返瞓咗幾個鐘, 跟住照呢個鐘數慢慢校返早瞓覺同起身時間<br />\n<br />\n夜瞓慣突然早咗瞓上床好易緊張同多嘢諗, 跟住夜晚容易發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fea0c7af4da0f1c01a9423fd542f7ede99fe2b7","tid":252888,"uid":52056,"l